January 24, 2018 / 3:28 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Regency Centers Acquires Two Adjacent Properties To Form Hewlett Crossing Reuters Staff 
Jan 24 (Reuters) - Regency Centers Corp: 
* REGENCY CENTERS ACQUIRES TWO ADJACENT PROPERTIES TO FORM HEWLETT CROSSING 
* REGENCY CENTERS CORP - ‍UNDER REGENCY‘S OWNERSHIP TWO WILL OPERATE AS A SINGLE CENTER KNOWN AS HEWLETT CROSSING​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
